Subject: [PATCH 006/987] Device tree entry for Freescale TDM controller

[Original patch taken from QorIQ-SDK-V1.6-SOURCE-20140619-yocto.iso]

Added dtsi file for Freescale TDM controller.
This controller is available on many Freescale SOCs like MPC8315, P1020, P1010,
P1022 and P1024
Signed-off-by: Sandeep Singh <Sandeep@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Poonam Aggrwal <poonam.aggrwal@freescale.com>
(cherry picked from commit e49da679e208b0fc275a38463d9455af5bbc798b)
